title: Renault Kwid E-TECH launched, gets 238 km battery range - Zee News
content: Renault Kwid E-TECH launched, gets 238 km battery range  Zee News
description: Renault Kwid E-TECH has safety features like tyre pressure monitoring system, six airbags, ABS, and more, and it can go 298 km on a single charge.
